---
title: "Sequence Diagram - Option 1: Add a Worker"
config:
  theme: neutral
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant V as WorkerView
    participant C as WorkerController
    participant M as Management

    User->>V: run program
    V->>User: display menu (1-5)
    User->>V: select option 1
    V-->>C: choice = 1
    C->>V: inputWorker()
    V->>User: prompt id, name, age, salary, work location
    User->>V: enter worker information
    V-->>C: return Worker object
    C->>M: addWorker(worker)
    M->>M: validateWorker(worker)

    alt id is null/empty or duplicated in DB
        M-->>C: throw Exception("Code is null or duplicated")
        C->>V: displayMessage(error)
        V->>User: show error message
    else age not in [18..50]
        M-->>C: throw Exception("Age must be 18-50")
        C->>V: displayMessage(error)
        V->>User: show error message
    else salary <= 0
        M-->>C: throw Exception("Salary must be > 0")
        C->>V: displayMessage(error)
        V->>User: show error message
    else data is valid
        M->>M: workerDB.put(id, worker)
        M-->>C: return true
        C->>V: displayMessage("Add worker successfully!")
        V->>User: show success message
    end

    C->>V: back to main screen
    V->>User: display menu (1-5)
